annotationA: Biogenesis of lysosome-related organelles complex 1 subunit 2; Component of the biogenesis of lysosome-related organelles complex-1 (BLOC-1) involved in pigment granule biogenesis
annotationB: Hermansky-Pudlak syndrome 5 protein homolog; Has a role in the biogenesis of eye pigment granules. Eye pigment granules are specialized forms of late endosomes or lysosomes. Biogenesis of pigment granules in the eye requires molecular components required for protein delivery to lysosomes
